	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />I know the square wave programmable timer is clocked by one APU cycle(equals two CPU cycles), the triangle wave programmable timer is clocked by one CPU cycle.<br />How about the noise wave programmable timer?<br />Thank you.

		

